<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣٨]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تَشْمِيتُ العَاطِسِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قَالَ النَّبِيُّ صلى الله عليه وسلم:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«إِذَا عَطَسَ أَحَدُكُمْ؛<span style="color:#006d98"> فَلْيَقُلْ:</span> الحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَلْيَقُلْ لَهُ أَخُوهُ أَوْ صَاحِبُهُ:</span> يَرْحَمُكَ اللَّهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَإِذَا قَالَ لَهُ:</span> يَرْحَمُكَ اللَّهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَلْيَقُلْ:</span> يَهْدِيكُمُ اللَّهُ، وَيُصْلِحُ بَالَكُمْ» <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>* * *<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) رَوَاهُ البُخَارِيُّ.</p> </div>